name: Air Squats
instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart. 2. Lower hips back and down as if sitting. 3. Keep chest up and knees behind toes. 4. Push through heels to return to start.

name: Arnold Press
instructions: Sit with dumbbells at shoulder height, palms facing you. 2. Press up while rotating palms forward. 3. Extend arms fully overhead. 4. Reverse motion to return.

name: Back Extensions
instructions: Lie face down on extension bench. 2. Cross arms over chest. 3. Lower torso down slowly. 4. Raise back up to neutral spine position.

name: Barbell Back Squat
instructions: Position barbell on upper back. 2. Stand with feet shoulder-width apart. 3. Lower down keeping chest up. 4. Drive through heels to stand.

name: Barbell Bench Press
instructions: Lie on bench with feet flat. 2. Grip barbell slightly wider than shoulders. 3. Lower bar to chest. 4. Press up to full extension.

name: Barbell Curl
instructions: Stand holding barbell with underhand grip. 2. Keep elbows close to sides. 3. Curl bar up to shoulders. 4. Lower with control.

name: Barbell Deadlift
instructions: Stand with feet hip-width, bar over midfoot. 2. Grip bar outside legs. 3. Lift by extending hips and knees. 4. Lower with control.

name: Barbell Row
instructions: Bend forward at hips with flat back. 2. Grip barbell with hands shoulder-width. 3. Pull bar to lower chest. 4. Lower with control.

name: Bench Dips
instructions: Place hands on bench behind you. 2. Extend legs forward. 3. Lower body by bending elbows. 4. Push back up to start.

name: Bicycle Crunches
instructions: Lie on back with hands behind head. 2. Bring opposite elbow to opposite knee. 3. Extend other leg straight. 4. Alternate sides in pedaling motion.

name: Cable Chest Fly
instructions: Stand between cable towers. 2. Hold handles with arms extended. 3. Bring hands together in arc motion. 4. Return with control.

name: Cable Tricep Pushdown
instructions: Face cable machine with high pulley. 2. Grip bar with overhand grip. 3. Push bar down by extending elbows. 4. Return with control.

name: Calf Raises
instructions: Stand with feet hip-width apart. 2. Rise up on toes as high as possible. 3. Hold briefly. 4. Lower with control.

name: Chair Pose (Yoga)
instructions: Stand with feet together. 2. Bend knees and lower hips as if sitting. 3. Raise arms overhead. 4. Hold position maintaining balance.

name: Chest Press Machine
instructions: Sit with back against pad. 2. Grip handles at chest level. 3. Push handles forward to full extension. 4. Return with control.

name: Chin-Ups
instructions: Hang from bar with underhand grip. 2. Pull body up until chin over bar. 3. Lower with control. 4. Repeat.

name: Clean and Press
instructions: Deadlift barbell to hips. 2. Pull bar explosively to shoulders. 3. Dip and drive bar overhead. 4. Lower to start position.

name: Close-Grip Bench Press
instructions: Lie on bench with hands closer than shoulder-width. 2. Lower bar to lower chest. 3. Press up focusing on triceps. 4. Maintain elbow position.

name: Concentration Curl
instructions: Sit with elbow braced against inner thigh. 2. Curl dumbbell up to shoulder. 3. Squeeze bicep at top. 4. Lower with control.

name: Crossover Crunch
instructions: Lie on back with hands behind head. 2. Bring right elbow to left knee. 3. Return to start. 4. Alternate sides.

name: Decline Bench Press
instructions: Lie on decline bench. 2. Grip barbell slightly wider than shoulders. 3. Lower to lower chest. 4. Press up to extension.

name: Diamond Push-Ups
instructions: Start in plank with hands forming diamond shape. 2. Lower chest to hands. 3. Keep elbows close to body. 4. Push back up.

name: Dumbbell Bench Press
instructions: Lie on bench with dumbbells at chest. 2. Press dumbbells up until arms extended. 3. Lower with control. 4. Keep movement smooth.

name: Dumbbell Flyes
instructions: Lie on bench with dumbbells above chest. 2. Lower arms in wide arc. 3. Feel stretch in chest. 4. Bring back to start.

name: Dumbbell Lunges
instructions: Hold dumbbells at sides. 2. Step forward into lunge. 3. Lower back knee toward ground. 4. Push back to start.

name: Dumbbell Shoulder Press
instructions: Sit with dumbbells at shoulders. 2. Press up to full extension. 3. Lower with control. 4. Keep core engaged.

name: Face Pulls
instructions: Face cable machine at upper height. 2. Pull rope toward face. 3. Separate hands at end. 4. Return with control.

name: Farmer's Walk
instructions: Hold heavy dumbbells at sides. 2. Walk forward with upright posture. 3. Keep core tight. 4. Take controlled steps.

name: Flutter Kicks
instructions: Lie on back with legs extended. 2. Lift legs slightly off ground. 3. Alternate kicking legs up and down. 4. Keep lower back pressed down.

name: Front Raises
instructions: Hold dumbbells in front of thighs. 2. Raise arms forward to shoulder height. 3. Keep slight bend in elbows. 4. Lower with control.

name: Front Squats
instructions: Rest barbell on front shoulders. 2. Cross arms to secure bar. 3. Squat down keeping chest up. 4. Drive through heels to stand.

name: Goblet Squats
instructions: Hold dumbbell at chest with both hands. 2. Squat down keeping elbows inside knees. 3. Keep chest up. 4. Stand back up.

name: Good Mornings
instructions: Place barbell on upper back. 2. Hinge forward at hips. 3. Keep back flat and legs mostly straight. 4. Return to standing.

name: Hack Squats
instructions: Position shoulders under pads. 2. Place feet on platform. 3. Lower body by bending knees. 4. Push up through heels.

name: Hammer Curls
instructions: Hold dumbbells with neutral grip. 2. Curl up keeping palms facing each other. 3. Squeeze at top. 4. Lower with control.

name: Handstand Push-Ups
instructions: Kick up into handstand against wall. 2. Lower head toward ground. 3. Press back up to full extension. 4. Maintain balance.

name: Hanging Leg Raises
instructions: Hang from bar with straight arms. 2. Raise legs to horizontal. 3. Lower with control. 4. Avoid swinging.

name: Hip Thrusts
instructions: Sit with upper back on bench. 2. Place barbell over hips. 3. Drive hips up to full extension. 4. Lower with control.

name: Incline Bench Press
instructions: Lie on incline bench. 2. Grip barbell slightly wider than shoulders. 3. Lower to upper chest. 4. Press up to extension.

name: Incline Dumbbell Curl
instructions: Sit on incline bench with arms hanging. 2. Curl dumbbells up. 3. Squeeze biceps at top. 4. Lower to full extension.

name: Inverted Rows
instructions: Hang under bar with body straight. 2. Pull chest to bar. 3. Keep body rigid. 4. Lower with control.

name: Jackknife Sit-Ups
instructions: Lie flat with arms overhead. 2. Simultaneously lift legs and torso. 3. Touch hands to feet. 4. Lower with control.

name: Kettlebell Deadlift
instructions: Stand with kettlebell between feet. 2. Hinge at hips to grip handle. 3. Stand up by extending hips. 4. Lower with control.

name: Knee Push-Ups
instructions: Start in plank on knees. 2. Lower chest to ground. 3. Keep body straight from knees to head. 4. Push back up.

name: Lat Pulldown
instructions: Sit at machine with thighs secured. 2. Grip bar wider than shoulders. 3. Pull bar down to upper chest. 4. Return with control.

name: Lateral Raises
instructions: Hold dumbbells at sides. 2. Raise arms out to sides to shoulder height. 3. Keep slight bend in elbows. 4. Lower with control.

name: Leg Curls
instructions: Lie face down on machine. 2. Place ankles under pad. 3. Curl legs toward glutes. 4. Lower with control.

name: Leg Extensions
instructions: Sit at machine with back against pad. 2. Place ankles under pad. 3. Extend legs to straight. 4. Lower with control.

name: Leg Press
instructions: Sit with feet on platform. 2. Release safety. 3. Lower platform by bending knees. 4. Push back to extension.

name: Leg Raises
instructions: Lie on back with legs straight. 2. Raise legs to 90 degrees. 3. Keep lower back pressed down. 4. Lower with control.

name: Lunges
instructions: Stand tall. 2. Step forward into lunge. 3. Lower back knee toward ground. 4. Push back to start.

name: Nordic Curls
instructions: Kneel with ankles secured. 2. Slowly lower torso forward. 3. Control descent with hamstrings. 4. Push back up.

name: Oblique Crunches
instructions: Lie on back with knees bent. 2. Crunch up and toward one side. 3. Squeeze oblique. 4. Alternate sides.

name: Overhead Press
instructions: Stand with barbell at shoulders. 2. Press bar overhead to full extension. 3. Keep core tight. 4. Lower to shoulders.

name: Overhead Squat
instructions: Hold barbell overhead with wide grip. 2. Squat down keeping bar over midfoot. 3. Maintain upright torso. 4. Stand back up.

name: Plank
instructions: Start in forearm position. 2. Keep body straight from head to heels. 3. Engage core. 4. Hold position.

name: Power Cleans
instructions: Deadlift barbell to knees. 2. Explosively pull bar up. 3. Drop under and catch at shoulders. 4. Stand to complete.

name: Preacher Curls
instructions: Rest arms on preacher bench. 2. Grip barbell with underhand grip. 3. Curl up to shoulders. 4. Lower to full extension.

name: Pull-Ups
instructions: Hang from bar with overhand grip. 2. Pull body up until chin over bar. 3. Lower with control. 4. Repeat.

name: Push-Ups
instructions: Start in plank position. 2. Lower chest to ground. 3. Keep body straight. 4. Push back up to start.

name: Quadruped Hip Extensions
instructions: Start on hands and knees. 2. Extend one leg back and up. 3. Squeeze glute at top. 4. Lower and repeat.

name: Reverse Crunches
instructions: Lie on back with knees bent. 2. Lift hips off ground toward chest. 3. Keep knees bent throughout. 4. Lower with control.

name: Reverse Flyes
instructions: Bend forward at hips. 2. Hold dumbbells hanging down. 3. Raise arms out to sides. 4. Lower with control.

name: Reverse Lunges
instructions: Stand tall. 2. Step back into lunge. 3. Lower back knee toward ground. 4. Push back to start.

name: Romanian Deadlift
instructions: Hold barbell at hips. 2. Hinge forward keeping legs mostly straight. 3. Lower bar to shins. 4. Return to standing.

name: Rope Climbing
instructions: Grip rope with both hands. 2. Use legs to clamp rope. 3. Pull body up hand over hand. 4. Climb to desired height.

name: Russian Twists
instructions: Sit with knees bent, feet off ground. 2. Lean back slightly. 3. Rotate torso side to side. 4. Touch ground beside hips.

name: Shoulder Shrugs
instructions: Hold dumbbells at sides. 2. Raise shoulders toward ears. 3. Hold briefly at top. 4. Lower with control.

name: Side Plank
instructions: Lie on side with elbow under shoulder. 2. Lift hips off ground. 3. Keep body straight. 4. Hold position.

name: Single-Leg Deadlift
instructions: Stand on one leg holding dumbbell. 2. Hinge forward extending free leg back. 3. Keep back flat. 4. Return to standing.

name: Sit-Ups
instructions: Lie on back with knees bent. 2. Place hands behind head. 3. Curl up to sitting position. 4. Lower with control.

name: Skull Crushers
instructions: Lie on bench holding barbell. 2. Lower bar to forehead by bending elbows. 3. Keep upper arms stationary. 4. Extend back up.

name: Sled Push
instructions: Grip sled handles. 2. Lean forward with arms extended. 3. Drive legs powerfully. 4. Push sled forward.

name: Split Squats
instructions: Stand in split stance. 2. Lower back knee toward ground. 3. Keep front knee behind toes. 4. Push back up.

name: Standing Calf Raises
instructions: Stand under shoulder pads. 2. Rise up on toes maximally. 3. Hold briefly. 4. Lower slowly.

name: Step-Ups
instructions: Place one foot on bench. 2. Push through heel to step up. 3. Bring other foot to bench. 4. Step down and repeat.

name: Sumo Deadlift
instructions: Stand with wide stance. 2. Grip bar with hands inside legs. 3. Lift by extending hips. 4. Lower with control.

name: Sumo Squats
instructions: Stand with wide stance, toes out. 2. Lower hips keeping knees over toes. 3. Keep torso upright. 4. Rise back up.

name: Superman Exercise
instructions: Lie face down with arms extended. 2. Lift arms and legs off ground. 3. Hold position. 4. Lower with control.

name: T-Bar Rows
instructions: Straddle barbell with chest supported. 2. Grip handles. 3. Pull bar to chest. 4. Lower with control.

name: Thruster
instructions: Hold barbell at shoulders. 2. Squat down. 3. Drive up and press bar overhead. 4. Lower to shoulders.

name: Tricep Dips
instructions: Grip parallel bars. 2. Lower body by bending elbows. 3. Keep elbows back. 4. Push back up.

name: Turkish Get-Up
instructions: Lie with kettlebell overhead. 2. Stand up while keeping bell overhead. 3. Reverse motion to lie back down. 4. Maintain control throughout.

name: Upright Rows
instructions: Hold barbell at thighs. 2. Pull bar up to chin level. 3. Keep elbows high. 4. Lower with control.

name: V-Ups
instructions: Lie flat with arms overhead. 2. Simultaneously lift legs and torso forming V. 3. Touch hands to feet. 4. Lower with control.

name: Wall Sit
instructions: Lean back against wall. 2. Lower into seated position. 3. Keep knees at 90 degrees. 4. Hold position.

name: Weighted Crunches
instructions: Lie on back holding weight on chest. 2. Crunch up keeping weight secure. 3. Squeeze abs at top. 4. Lower with control.

name: Wide-Grip Pull-Ups
instructions: Hang from bar with wide overhand grip. 2. Pull body up to bar. 3. Focus on lat engagement. 4. Lower with control.

name: Wood Choppers
instructions: Stand sideways to cable machine. 2. Pull cable from high to low across body. 3. Rotate torso. 4. Control return.

name: Wrist Curls
instructions: Rest forearms on bench with wrists hanging. 2. Curl weights up using wrists. 3. Squeeze forearms. 4. Lower with control.
